      <title>美联储会议纪要显示，鲍威尔降息 50 个基点遭到抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/fed-minutes-show-pushback-on-powell-s-50-bps-rate-cut-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 9 月将利率下调半个百分点，遭到了一些反对，因为一些官员更倾向于将利率下调幅度缩小至四分之一个百分点。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/fed-minutes-show-pushback-on-powell-s-50-bps-rate-cut-video</guid>
