      <title>资金充裕的婴儿潮一代吸引投资者，而澳大利亚年轻人则承担了重担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cashed-up-boomers-draw-investors-as-young-aussies-bear-the-load</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者纷纷抢购面向富裕退休人群的澳大利亚股票，同时避开面向年轻家庭的公司，这一现象加剧了代际财富差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cashed-up-boomers-draw-investors-as-young-aussies-bear-the-load</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
